description: Enables or disables debugging over Wi-Fi Allows you to enable or disable ADB debugging over TCP (i.e. Wi-Fi) from within the device, without having to connect it to your machine via USB. Features: * Easily turn wireless debugging on or off by flipping a switch * Prevent device from sleeping while debugging * Automatically turn off debugging on screen lock * Displays a status notification with Wi-Fi connection info and a stop button
